<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- mạbttnsysẖ dh ạ̹nt ạ̹lhy wạ̉bwyạ gẖyrk mạlysẖ
 mạbttnsysẖ dh ạsmy mnswb ʿly̱ ạsmk wmʿạk bạʿysẖ
 1- sạnd ly ʿmry wḥyạty dạry bkl ạḥtyạjạty
 fạkr ṣlạty wṭlbạty mạbtnsạnysẖ
 wṭwl mạ ạ̉nạ mạsẖy fy ḍlk wsẖkr qlb bywṣl lk
 tmly fạkrk wbạqwlk mạbttnsysẖ
 2- wlw ʿly ḥrwb qạmt wạ̉nạ lʿjzy bqyt ṣạmt
 lw ạ̉my nsytny wnạmt mạbtnsạnysẖ
 yạrb lmạ tḍyq by ạ̉lqy̱ lfwq rạyḥẗ ʿyny
 lạ̉nk ạ̹nt yạ rạʿy mạbttnsysẖ
 3- ṣlbk ʿlsẖạny byạ̉srny ạ̹nt bjlạlk tkẖtạrny tbqy̱ ạ̹nt rby ạlly fạkrny mạbtnsạnysẖ
 mʿqwl yạrby ạ̉nsy̱ fdạk ạ̉nạ ạ̉nsy̱ nfsy wlạ ạ̉nsạk
 dy kl nqṭẗ mn dmạk mạbttnsysẖ</lyrics>
<title>mạbttnsysẖ</title>
